1. On je postao* predsednik jedne teško pogođene zemlje. (He became the president of a severely affected country.)
2. Ona je postala* uspešna umetnica. (She became a successful artist.)
3. Oni će postati* najveći svetski lideri. (They will become the greatest world leaders.)
4. Oni će postati* svesni svojih odgovornosti. (They will become aware of their responsibilities.)
5. Ona će postati* najbolja u svojoj klasi. (She will become the best in her class.)
6. On će postati* poznat kao najbolji doktor. (He will become known as the best doctor.)